{"tid":1547204,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對於每晚10點演唱會有以下睇法","createTime":"2019-09-06T15:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T15:06:38.000Z","uid":121005,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e610719f7665a996f43ef934b287ab3d5b80c924","tid":1547204,"uid":121005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:03:24.000Z","msg":"首先我無權阻止每區嘅手足喺自己住所叫口號, 雖然夜晚10點對於好香港人黎講仲係好早,甚至有好多仲喺度開緊工或搏命ot緊,但係對於一d需要早睡早起返工嘅市民的確做成滋擾。<br />\n我住大埔狗屋附近嘅,因為工作需要,每晚都由9點半訓教,淩晨4點起身返工。你可以話返工大撚晒呀!自私鬼!<br />\n我依家答你:係呀！香港人真係好鍾意返工架!<br />\n由最初只係短暫互相叫口號,發展到每晚都有街坊同手足互相指罵,時間長短每晚有所唔同。我住果座大廈都有幾位人士同我立場相同,工作時間相約,但都對呢個活動開始反感。<br />\n我希望演唱會發起人,好好考慮一下,發起演唱會目的係乜野,呢個活動仲應唔應該繼續落去或者點樣行落去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:<br />\n唔收貨<br />\n五大訴求, 缺一不可<br />\n黑警還眼"},{"pid":"d3c9b4437b97703e211164faede4ea6e22345668","tid":1547204,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:04:51.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"203e1a26ffa7eb15f66e98ad1fbe1af7a73a7bd5","tid":1547204,"uid":121966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ymz9rQj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYmz9rQj.jpg&h=ded89aca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3f19190cf7ba47400f3e6551d1157ad91c72025","tid":1547204,"uid":1870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:06:16.000Z","msg":"提早9點鐘會唔會好D?"},{"pid":"b4b0e8ea4ffa079a6d553453b14d9207b4c6d231","tid":1547204,"uid":94982